      "text": [
        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مِنْ سَعَادَةِ اَلرَّجُلِ أَنْ لاَ تَحِيضَ اِبْنَتُهُ فِي بَيْتِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4647 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) said: \"Part of a man's happiness is that his daughter does not experience menstruation in his house.\""
        ]
      }
